        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Esdrius Stai <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> domo Bri<lb break="no" n="3"/>xia <expan><abbr>Fab</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> tubicen <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>coho</abbr><ex>rtis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Mon</abbr><ex>tanorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXV <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>XIIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Verdavi duo <lb n="8"/>cognati <lb n="9"/>posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: 1977 oder 1978. Nach Scherrer sehr wahrscheinlich eine moderne &amp;lt;span style=&amp;apos;color:red&amp;apos;&amp;gt;Fälschung&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;. Peregriner mit domus und tribus. Im Giebel oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes eine Rosette, Eidechse(?) und Zikade(?).</p>
            </div>
